         Nope my point stands. Consider this argument. If I have a Nuclear weapon and my next door neighbour has a Biological weapon, who will kill more people?. The argument is moot because neither of us have Nuclear or Bio weapons.</P><P>If I own an M60 and he owns an RPD, then we can have an argument that makes sense.</P><P>Extend it out. Me and my neighbour are in the pub continuing our Nuke/Bio argument. All of our friends and relatives are there as well, but they only own hand weapons. How interested are they going to be in our argument as they dont own and will never own said weapons.</P><P>Its the same thing.</P><P>Warlock<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=49001" target="_blank">Profile</a><BR><a href="http://www.domain-admins.com/Necro/index.shtml" target="_blank">Ulaa's web site</a><BR><img src="http://www.sizzlesites.com/Ulaa/steve.jpg"</img><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
