        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I agree with Dolalin.</P><P>I just want to point out:</P><P>If you look at the wizard's lvl60 spells, you'll notice they've been given a 1615dmg Fire DD, a 1200dmg Ice DD, an 1890dmg MR DD, and a 2100dmg Fire DD.</P><P>They have lvl60 Fire, Ice, and Magic based nukes.</P><P>Now if you look at our lvl60 spells, you'll see that we get a 2160dmg Fire DoT.</P><P>That's... it.</P><P>The level 60 game is becoming very common and very important in EQ. Wizards have top of the line nukes AT 60 making them very powerful. We have one.</P><P>I'm hoping that PoP will introduce more lvl60 DoTs for us. We just need to get upgrades to our DoT lines, at 60, and maybe even a new Cold line.</P><P>~ <b>Xarslik Malarslik</b> ~<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=263077">My Gear</a><BR>Iksar Warlock of the Seventh Hammer<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
