        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         If they ever do allow us to self stack our own DoTs, that buff limit would have to be further extended.  Honestly I do not know why there is one at all, the limit of buffs on the mob should be in the hundereds not 15 or even 30.  Atm since our best dot has a duration of 54 seconds, and 1 necro could stack 9 DoT's on him, honestly the Max buff slots would have to be extended to around 180, this would allow 20 necros to stack all 9 DoT's.  There will doubtfully be any raid with 20 necro's, as unlikely as there would be a raid with 20 wizards, but that's the point, allow necro's to do their job if they want.</P><P>Reepr<BR>Warlock of Lanys<BR><Sigil><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
